articles.author: Heidi Parker
articles.title: Spider-Man 4 still happening says producer Amy Pascal - Daily Mail
articles.description: Pascal confirmed to Variety that though the highly anticipated sequel has been stalled due to the writers strike, it is still very much in the works. No release date is set yet.
articles.content:
Spider-Man 4 is still happening.
